            Our <span class="text-primary-600">Project Methodology</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8">
            Every project follows our proven methodology ensuring quality,
            safety, and timely delivery.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div
                class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-lg"
              >
                <span class="text-xl font-bold">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                  Consultation & Planning
